{"tid":1303126,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"琼子：社會對立，撕裂嚴重，目睹暴力，感到痛心","createTime":"2019-07-10T07:58:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T14:07:51.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3748df6f96db7dfea9c1836b38a794ec4e75b72e","tid":1303126,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T07:58:43.000Z","msg":"今天是民建聯成立27周年，民建聯主席李慧琼表示，香港正經歷一浪又一浪的衝突，<span style=\"color: red;\">社會對立，撕裂嚴重，尤其是當目睹一星期前立法會受到暴力破壞的情景，更是感到痛心</span>。<br />\n<br />\n她指出，在任何時候，表達不同意見，爭取不同訴求，都必須採取和平理性的方法。違法暴力是行不通的，理性溝通才是出路。特區政府已明確指出修訂《逃犯條例》的工作已經停止，民建聯希望和社會各界朋友同心協力，為特區政府改善施政、發展民生經濟，提供最有力的支持，理性務實地幫香港走出對立。<br />\n<br />\n今天亦是DSE放榜日，李慧琼稱，成績理想固然替大家高興；即使未如理想，仍有很多可以選擇的出路，一時的失意，不用灰心、氣餒，未來仍有很長的路要走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187980/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2187980%2F&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5sm%2Bn8Fwo%2F6aJUx9arcu0Q%3D&h=d418e88f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2187980/</a>"},{"pid":"838513a1d21216c8188ff5934d800843ed64a83a","tid":1303126,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:01:25.000Z","msg":"究竟琼子痛心咗幾多次"},{"pid":"0393de4be392f2df899aafbcf564c4d54563844d","tid":1303126,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38942300ee7e72ccee23d23973b4c6fc9aac3ed3","tid":1303126,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:12:38.000Z","msg":"民建聯係社會撕裂嘅主要推手喎"},{"pid":"45a1aecc062fd6447e3b5cf349c984b15f46ea97","tid":1303126,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:08:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8c467aa12841b701d66dc651db16d54f63ecf8","tid":1303126,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0